HEADWORD: Coastways
<hw>Coast"ways`</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>adv.</pos> <def>By way of, or along, the
coast; following a coastline; <as>as, <ex>coastwise</ex> winds
contributed to the storm</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

